{"tid":393803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"先安內而後攘外(自身卦)免費占卜","createTime":"2017-09-09T13:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T23:56:30.000Z","uid":129128,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd4afc5b9b60a82529e606f2d9c7f177b1b0804","tid":393803,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"自身卦係一種好大範圍嘅事，但會離唔開你日常生活嘅事，都可以係一種修心嘅卦，從而改善運氣<br />\n只占一事，有咩事都可以占，但唔占賭博，同埋會打比你講返比你知，因為比較詳細啲，問問題一定要詳細<br />\n留低你中文全名，出生日期，男定女，問咩事，盡量全部都占<br />\n可以占孕婦，官司，失物/人，家居風水，，買樓租樓，生意，出門遠行，自身卦，奇難集症等等等等<br />\n未夠18歲唔占<br />\nwhatsapp 59891042"},{"pid":"e0e76c00c58e973d4a909e6b02729659e87b6de5","tid":393803,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3aed03dbb431708636779a847f99edbc5e214a1e","tid":393803,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0882740d4c58d1164d5a9b5b1adfb0ab9405a7b","tid":393803,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51932c8735c64894328a1b7616c9362c37911dc2","tid":393803,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:16:30.000Z","msg":"whatsapp你？"},{"pid":"bc4fb7eaea0ea6f5819415d8fae15acd137f19c9","tid":393803,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>whatsapp你？</blockquote><br />\nSure"},{"pid":"4199aa41023c73ebb047228396808c262a0b8ecb","tid":393803,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4adc363362f5670995b6ae2f347d85b679d452","tid":393803,"uid":140112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:18:22.000Z","msg":"想知樓主你係點起卦？@@"},{"pid":"2971377836fd630bf98de339cbb21ec00f5b7f6e","tid":393803,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike